Description: # shows
        lib for system monitoring with CPU/GPU/DISK/MEM/NET
        
        ## install
        `pip install shows`
        
        ## usage
        ### bash
        after installation, type the following in your terminal:
        ```bash
        shows
        ```
        
        ### python
        ```python
        import shows
        machine  = shows.machine()
        machine.get_state()
        ```
        
